description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. A new take on the classic game Snake. The CyberSnake is a prototype circuit build and repair program being put to the test in a crisis which could wipe out everyone within proximity.
